				                <div>Hello Ernest,<br />
<br />
When you get this type of error, take a look at the message itself. It will give you a place to start troubleshooting in your query. Your message says the error occurs "<strong>near 'ORDER BY content.created DESC' at line 25</strong>" so you want to check right around that area of your query.<br />
<br />
In your query around that area, you have "<em>WHERE ORDER BY content.created DESC</em>".<br />
<br />
The <em>WHERE</em> is needing something after it. It is expecting some sort of argument or parameter before the <em>ORDER BY</em> is performed. The <em>WHERE</em> portion filters the data set down, for example if you wanted to list all customers with the last name of 'Smith' you would have a <em>WHERE</em> portion of your query that looked something like:<br />
<div class="code_block">WHERE last_name="Smith"</div><br />
In some cases, you may not need a <em>WHERE</em> clause, if you want to list all customers and order them, you would simply leave off the <em>WHERE</em> portion.<br />
<div class="code_block">SELECT first_name, last_name FROM customers ORDER BY last_name</div><br />
So, if that is the case with your query, simply remove the '<em>WHERE</em>' from your query and that should cause the error to go away.<br />
<br />
Kindest Regards,<br />
Scott M <br />
