				                <div>Hello Keith,<br />
<br />
The error message means that there is a syntax error in the MySQL query that Joomla is attempting to run. This is normally an easier type of error to fix if you coded the query yourself. If you did not and it is coming from the application itself, such as Joomla, then this can be extremely nerve racking. All I can do is attempt to help you understand the error and then you can either attempt to fix it or find someone who can track it down and fix it within the application.<br />
<br />
The error message gives you an idea of where the error occurs in the statement. In your particular case it is around the section in the query where 'AND memberid=357' is located. The error then gives the full query it is attempting to run: "<em>DELETE FROM wz4rx_community_groups_members WHERE groupid= AND memberid=357</em>"  If you look closely, just before the "<em>AND memberid=357</em>" portion you can see it says "<em>WHERE groupid=</em>". Note that there is no value for<em>groupid</em>. This is what is causing the error.  <br />
<br />
So, whatever is supposed to be deleted is either missing a groupid or the code is not placing the groupid in the query properly.<br />
<br />
Kindest Regards,<br />
